<br>
1. ALL people should have resists over 100 UNBUFFED.  This will help to reduce damage taken by all the AE mobs and therefore save some mana from the healers.  With the BD's that now drop in the PoP zones, this should be a little less costly than before.<br>
<br>
2. Casters should always sit around the corner (not too close to the pit so as to avoid aggro) and step out when casting.  Again, this reduces the chance for damage.  When the mob gets close enough that casters take damage, switch to the other corner.<br>
<br>
